{"tid":1010274,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"韓國瑜早有總統視野格局？網友翻出他20年前政見","createTime":"2019-02-06T00:55:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-06T04:08:16.000Z","uid":35790,"like":4,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e968e546a949f7127703f6e80d95be25f388a429","tid":1010274,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T00:55:39.000Z","msg":"韓國瑜早有總統視野格局？網友翻出他20年前政見<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2019-02-02/656/20190202001821.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2019-02-02%2F656%2F20190202001821.jpg&h=c74b2791&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n高雄市長韓國瑜，早年擔任立法委員時照片。<br />\n<br />\n高雄市長韓國瑜從政之路雖長遠，但一路走來可說是相當坎坷，從政後曾任第12屆臺北縣議員，及三屆立法委員，還曾任中和副市長，地方中央經歷還算完整，但有網友翻出，韓國瑜20年前參選立委時的政見，原來韓國瑜早有大格局。<br />\n<br />\n有網友在《mobile01》上找出韓國瑜20年前的選舉公報，即1998年韓國瑜參選立委時的政見，認為韓國瑜那時已有總統格局，20年前的政見到現在都適用。當年韓國瑜主推「3大反對，5大要求」，分別是「反對台獨、反對分化、反對貪腐」，以及「強化治安、幼兒福祉、經濟景氣、人民權益、慈善宗教」，還主張「治亂世用重典」。提出鞭刑、強暴累犯去勢等嚴刑，更是令人不寒而慄。<br />\n<br />\n對於台灣目前的少子化議題，韓國瑜當時主張，應該廣設幼托中心、推動幼托合一。在社會福利部份，他則贊成應提升軍公教福利及中醫藥地位，並幫助社會弱勢。而在政治議題上，韓國瑜則主張「反對急統及台獨」。<br />\n<br />\n而一眾網友看到這20年前的政見被翻出，不僅沒有撻伐韓國瑜，反而<span style=\"color: red;\">大讚這「20年前的政見到現在都適用」，紛紛表示，「這選總統應該高票當選了」</span>、「20年前就知道統獨玩假的，意識形態拖累台灣」、「可能要改喊選總統了」、「20年前就想到要鞭刑廢物跟強暴犯去勢，真有遠見」、「這選總統應該高票當選了」。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20190206000026-260407\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Frealtimenews%2F20190206000026-260407&d=fwxP8pl6u%2F9ArYBpkrNVTGipy2YcCk4ac690EPkq9Sw%3D&h=3df0b857\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20190206000026-260407</a><br />\n中時不停鼓吹<br />\n證明支那瑜背後。。。"},{"pid":"e920a2c10879eb4bf461fb7053e6d736da604f28","tid":1010274,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T00:56:32.000Z","msg":"支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c562250a1f6ad6b25e019479301331a53cc0b230","tid":1010274,"uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T00:58:26.000Z","msg":"期望支那瑜代表kmt參選總統<br />\n一統天下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6f40482fa1b9b6c2d32513eefffe1263a5970e7","tid":1010274,"uid":8810,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T01:00:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">台灣<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">特區</span></span>發大財</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41fde050b8ad4b983c5dae405ee420d5602c6468","tid":1010274,"uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T01:03:31.000Z","msg":"特首支那瑜領導下<br />\n中國台灣發大財"},{"pid":"4d6d586dc92776082d8e452736ee096608641526","tid":1010274,"uid":3067,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T01:24:47.000Z","msg":"20年前就已經開始 鳩嗡"},{"pid":"8723954ab6940e24833a307970ca99d18a083072","tid":1010274,"uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4d6d586dc92776082d8e452736ee096608641526","tid":1010274,"uid":3067,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T01:24:47.000Z","msg":"20年前就已經開始 鳩嗡"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T01:29:27.000Z","msg":"文武兼備<br />\n當立委時立法院開會打到阿扁入廠"},{"pid":"fe97f1eaa1d443aa42bb92ab1f0949c9ea37158d","tid":1010274,"uid":85116,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T01:34:35.000Z","msg":"佢係唔係食左十幾年軟飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4f829cc708c9eabb34db5ef6a56e740ed65c83a","tid":1010274,"uid":47492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8723954ab6940e24833a307970ca99d18a083072","tid":1010274,"uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4d6d586dc92776082d8e452736ee096608641526","tid":1010274,"uid":3067,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-06